Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛偽的結合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,竟然淋得這麼濕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才要您別去管,那個女人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我回房去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心別感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你就早點休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天還得參加蜜拉娜公主的婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:02:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差點就能贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過上次比幸運時是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們就扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你神氣成這樣是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為確實是我贏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人的嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很溫暖?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓我感覺一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想得到弗肯大人的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒那個吻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就還能繼續作夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人雖然待我們很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻沒有感受到愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,還是很幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:04:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那時候我們原本就該死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們必定經歷過艱辛的命運吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你們取個新名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們從今天開始重生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願你們能被幸運所眷顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明明已經得到幸運了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻還是…勝不過龍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你們現在的幸運等級
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確超越不了他的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你們如此希望\N那我就給予你們更多的幸運吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保證不會輸給任何人所向披靡的幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得明明有個很相襯的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地鼠先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主您…該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時的那種光芒感不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就擔心您是不是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物雖然有許多種
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最適合自己的卻總是只有一個而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你們全身的血液全都換成幸運血液
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運血液?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據多倫卡喀大人的研究結果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選出寨巴哈境內特別好運存活機率高的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從其細胞核中萃取出幸運去氧核糖核酸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再經由命運改變裝置的力量所合成的人工血液
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險性極高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一個環節出錯就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是幸運的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運強化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜她這樣做真的好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說…小瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼到現在才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我不確定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己是否真的能跟德萊甸一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…又不是成田離婚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成田離婚?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是你只是婚前憂鬱罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚前憂鬱?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之,我已經沒辦法再幫人算命了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當是幫個忙為我算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一我又招來奇怪的未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論結果如何我都相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨龍3
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒吊之男
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷,網
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她果然對這場政治聯姻感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想要逃離這股壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…婚姻本來就有各種狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然決定要結婚,你會不安也是在所難免
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能因此而急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏的A
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚5
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野獸5
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣結婚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會因為身邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被捲入極度的傷痛與紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚姻生活中或許會出現一些小障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩壞之塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是這場婚姻是再糟糕不過的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我把這個結果告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定會決定不結婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表著幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是我用了這張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許就能招來這樣的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要運用意念之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以招來更好的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只要強烈地希望著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必定就能改變命運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.12,0:11:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張牌代表幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:12:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說,你和德萊甸結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和德萊甸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜,掌握幸運吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在唸咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒語?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望蜜拉娜與德萊甸能夠幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:14:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身處日月風水恩典豐饒的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位聰慧的阿斯多利亞子民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們將迎接這個神聖嶄新的時刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於龍與少女斷絕了聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得確率密度安定下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是捕獲改變命運的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕獲神崎瞳的絕佳機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍的影響如果再出現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時將龍除掉就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您不用擔心,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的幸運已是無敵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必定會捕獲神崎瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然和我第一次的占卜結果一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悍馬公主這下也要成為人妻了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場婚不能結
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是王兄的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍居然主動告知所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運等級確實提升了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?小瞳?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不能接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會在這種時候發生日蝕?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍來襲,敵軍來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈為什麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝甲隊出動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在這種緊要關頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德萊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能讓你接近神崎瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是幸運強化的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德萊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太丟臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德萊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就暫時不要緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯嘉科尼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是寨巴哈的幸運強化兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬告阿斯多利亞的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一遍\N王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是寨巴哈的幸運強化兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運…強化兵\N敬告阿斯多利亞的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運…\N抵抗只會白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說的幸運該不會就是這張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必將面臨恐怖之不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用這張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變了命運
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我將命運調換所以才會發生這種事?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只有一個要求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是交出幻之月少女,神崎瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是不想面臨更嚴重之不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就馬上將神崎瞳交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能出去,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德萊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我在占卜時造假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造假?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這場婚事的占卜結果並不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻以為能夠改變它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為能用意念之力改變它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正適合你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我喜歡亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不想失戀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就將占卜的結果…將命運給調換了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德萊甸,德萊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是幻之月少女,神崎瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:22:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你就是不懂呢?梵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運的反作用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:57.39,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:05.84,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:13.47,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:19.62,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:21.98,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:26.99,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃燒般的神秘雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:30.83,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真無邪的笑容讓我傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:34.63,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深處的暗示只傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:38.64,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了無止盡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.70,0:22:42.14,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的鼓動無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:49.61,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想帶著你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:57.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:05.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:13.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:19.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.68,0:22:21.98,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:26.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:30.82,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:34.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:38.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.70,0:22:42.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:49.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい

